# FTGO CODEOWNERS
# ---------------
# GitHub enforces a review from at least one owner on every path below.
# Patterns are evaluated top-to-bottom; the last matching pattern wins, so
# keep the most specific entries at the bottom of each section.
#
# Teams referenced here live under the @ftgo-project GitHub organization.
# Create the team before merging — an unknown team name silently fails
# and every PR becomes an unowned change.
#
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

